## Ignore Visual Studio temporary files, build results, and
## files generated by popular Visual Studio add-ons.
##
## This .gitignore file has been tailored for .NET/C# projects.
## For more info, see: https://github.com/github/gitignore/blob/main/VisualStudio.gitignore

# [Visual Studio]
.vs/
[Oo]bj/
[Bb]in/
*.user
*.suo
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

# [JetBrains Rider]
.idea/
*.sln.iml

# [Visual Studio Code]
.vscode/

# [User-specific files]
*.rsuser
*.suo
*.user
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

# [Build results]
[Dd]ebug/
[Dd]ebugPublic/
[Rr]elease/
[Rr]eleases/
x64/
x86/
[Aa][Rr][Mm]/
[Aa][Rr][Mm]64/
bld/
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/
[Log]/

# [Docker]
.dockerignore

# [OS generated files]
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
